1. On *vrti* ključ u bravi. (He is turning the key in the lock.)
2. *Vrti* se kao na ringišpilu. (She is spinning like on a carousel.)
3. Kada *vrtim* ovaj gumb, ništa se ne dešava. (When I turn this button, nothing happens.)
4. U krug *se vrti* dok ne pronađe pravu riječ. (She spins in circles until she finds the right word.)
5. Koliko puta sam ti rekao da *ne vrtiš* novac u džepu? (How many times have I told you not to spin money in your pocket?)
6. *Vrti* se ploča na gramofonu. (The record is spinning on the turntable.)
7. Oni *se vrteli* u društvu slavnih i bogatih. (They circulated in the company of famous and wealthy people.)
8. Deca *vrtića* su se igrala napolju. (Kindergarten children were playing outside.)
9. Ona *vrti* restoran sa svojim mužem. (She runs a restaurant with her husband.)
10. Možeš li mi *zavrnuti* šraf na biciklu? (Can you tighten the screw on the bike for me?)